{"tid":2411154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新冠病毒株竟合體！加州首現「變種病毒組合」　傳染性和抗藥性高","createTime":"2021-02-17T06:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T22:52:45.000Z","uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d1285f15bc41a3a54edbedd9fea240a2241e0681","tid":2411154,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtJ6J3v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtJ6J3v.jpg&h=345f9e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RiLXQJw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRiLXQJw.jpg&h=56565128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://f.share.photo.xuite.net/dav912/1fcd3fe/14749454/782898160_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fdav912%2F1fcd3fe%2F14749454%2F782898160_m.jpg&h=2a04b47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者葉睿涵／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國加州洛斯阿拉莫斯國家實驗室 (Los Alamos National Laboratory)最近發現，英國的新冠變種病毒株「B.1.1.7」已和來自加州的新變種病毒株「B.1.429」結合，形成變種病毒組合。科學家們擔心，這種變種病毒組合將演變成傳染性和抗藥性更強的新變種病毒，進而讓大流行進入新階段。<br />\n<br />\n據《太陽報》和《洛杉磯時報》報導，目前科學家們還不清楚新的變種病毒組合會帶來多大的威脅，但這是人類第一次在新冠疫情爆發後，發現2種不同變種病毒株合體成組合的現象。發現此現象的計算生物學家科伯（Bette Korber）表示，變種病毒組合同時具有讓病毒更具傳讓性的B.1.1.7變種病毒，和可以和抗體對抗的B.1.429變種病毒，這可能讓變種病毒組合的傳染性和抗藥性來得更高。<br />\n<br />\n研究也指出，變種病毒組合的出現意味著部分患者可能感染了2種不同的病毒株。賓州天普大學（Temple University）的生物學教授龐德（Sergei Pond）表示，「當這種情況以可觀的速度發生時，那疫情可能就要到達臨界點了。」不過他認為，目前還沒有證據顯示，變種病毒組合已廣泛傳播，但冠狀病毒之間產生結合現象其實非常普遍。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 新冠病毒株竟合體！加州首現「變種病毒組合」 傳染性和抗藥性高 | ETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210217/1920566.htm#ixzz6mhojmrAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210217%2F1920566.htm%23ixzz6mhojmrAg&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=7fec31fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210217/1920566.htm#ixzz6mhojmrAg</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"61e27850dc64eec72534617111af2c926700b187","tid":2411154,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://irregular.enzan.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%AB%E6%97%A5-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Firregular.enzan.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%2597%25A5-1024x576.jpg&h=10102679&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1025162e50b41fc0a5cf5bc4b591fac3b17b3422","tid":2411154,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"印度神童.jpg"},{"pid":"b10e7e27a974384c2bc6397facd2b207ef90bdba","tid":2411154,"uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"夠點未升<br />\n點左抗藥同空氣傳播"},{"pid":"3a46d9afad47adbebc57de06f5705f056ce6d4f9","tid":2411154,"uid":20563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b10e7e27a974384c2bc6397facd2b207ef90bdba","tid":2411154,"uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"夠點未升<br />\n點左抗藥同空氣傳播"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"儲多陣氣，點埋出下冷汗再爆上去出肺氣泡<br />\n同時間點埋多種病株，阻埋實驗室研發"},{"pid":"2c7e12ba79f3e445223efdb359935dd9982a0e75","tid":2411154,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"deep state玩夠未？"},{"pid":"7ca36175a1e4e5a9fe9242326a2b96e0261bbe2c","tid":2411154,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db44a5b69a8d1e51b078814b10ef59a29dd225cd","tid":2411154,"uid":25